codeText: public final File getValidDirectory() {_		File file = this.directory__		file = (file != null ? file : getWarFileDocumentRoot())__		file = (file != null ? file : getExplodedWarFileDocumentRoot())__		file = (file != null ? file : getCommonDocumentRoot())__		if (file == null && this.logger.isDebugEnabled()) {_			logNoDocumentRoots()__		}_		else if (this.logger.isDebugEnabled()) {_			this.logger.debug("Document root: " + file)__		}_		return file__	}
